                                                  2017</ref>)</sourceNote><section id="ID_1438402799635_002" name="s1" reason="inEffect" role="regulation" startPeriod="2017-11-16" status="operational" temporalId="s1"><num value="1">1.</num><heading>Citation</heading><content>These regulations may be cited as the Births and Deaths Registration (Description of Causes of Death) Regulations.</content></section><section id="ID_1438402799635_004" name="s2" reason="inEffect" role="regulation" startPeriod="2017-11-16" status="operational" temporalId="s2"><num value="2">2.</num><heading>Description according to W.H.O.’s 3-Digit List</heading><content>For the purpose of paragraph (d) of <ref>section 20</ref> of the Births and Deaths
            Registration Ordinance (<ref href="/hk/cap174">Cap. 174</ref>), causes of death shall be
            described in accordance with the Detailed List of Three-Digit Categories (3位數字詳細分類表) set
            out in the Manual of the International Statistical Classification of Diseases, Injuries
            and Causes of Death
            (國際病症、損傷及死亡原因統計分類手冊),
            published by or by arrangement with the World Health Organization and as the same may
            from time to time be revised. </content></section></main></subLeg>